00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:41,940
which runs

484
00:28:41,940 --> 00:28:43,420
over 700 li,

485
00:28:43,420 --> 00:28:44,900
chasing the sun across the sky.

486
00:28:45,060 --> 00:28:46,100
The mighty stag

487
00:28:46,260 --> 00:28:47,940
