500
00:29:12,100 --> 00:29:12,940
and stops at Rongjun,

501
00:29:13,460 --> 00:29:15,020
improving the traffic condition,

502
00:29:15,620 --> 00:29:17,940
encouraging peace,
and driving away the spiteful.

